@Thoughtfulnz @CarlosMCorderoB This type of lagged trend is seen in other countries quite commonly with Omicron. Acute stage is less severe ("mild" as it is advertised to be) but health system is not clear of it . Seen in kids more then with other variants eg US, India, S Africa off the top of my head.
@Thoughtfulnz Soooo, it’s still all happening then.
